Facebook post by Noorie Noor Ananta, 25 November 2016. Hindi/Hinglish text: 'Abhi toh sirf 500 aur 1000k note hi boriyoo m bhar bhar k log fekh rhe hai.... Ab Gold fekhne k liye bhi jagah dudegee.... 88' Translation: 'Right now people are throwing away 500 and 1000 notes in sacks... Soon they'll need space to throw away gold too... 88.' DECODED: '88' = double emphasis on the number 8 (Nov 8). Gold prediction — prophesying that after cash demonetization, gold hoarding will also be targeted. This is a forward-looking prophecy beyond demonetization. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Coded Signals — predicting the next wave of cosmic justice targeting gold/black wealth.